Catalog contains programs:

-----Program 1 handles signal in chosen way (d - default action, i - ignoring, p - signal interception)
    -> To run use command make run1 ARGS="arg1 arg2" (arg1 - choosing action, arg2 - signal number)

-----Program 2 runs program 1 using exec function and sends signal to program 1 (d - default action, i - ignoring, p - signal interception)
    ->To run use command make run2 ARGS="arg1 arg2" (arg1 - choosing action, arg2 - signal number)

-----Program 3 creates child process, which creates child processes,which run program 1 (d - default action, i - ignoring, p - signal interception)
    ->To run use command make run3 ARGS="arg1 arg2" (arg1 - choosing action, arg2 - signal number)

==============================================================================================================
     Cleaning
    -> make clean
    
     Archivization 
    -> make tar
==============================================================================================================

